@startuml
title Facility Administrator View Conflict Report
actor Admin
participant "Web App" as WA
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "App Server" as AS
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> WA: Login with credentials
WA -> API: Send login request
API -> AS: Authenticate admin
AS -> DB: Validate credentials
DB --> AS: Return authentication status
AS --> API: Authentication result
API --> WA: Return login success

WA -> API: Request facility conflict reports
API -> AS: Fetch conflict reports
AS -> DB: Read facility bookings & detect conflicts
DB --> AS: Return conflict report data
AS --> API: Return conflict reports
API --> WA: Display conflict reports
WA --> Admin: Show facility conflict dashboard
@enduml